\s Guh 203 MUNSI Y’AMABABA YE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Munsi y’amababa ye nihw’ ampisha, N’ubw’ ijoro ryakwijima cyane, ntacyo nzatinya nzi kw’azankomeza, ubu nd’umwana We Yacunguye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Munsi y’ayo mababa Ye, havuy’ Urukundo rwinshi, Mu mababa niho nzibera, mu mahor’iteka ryose.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Munsi y’amababa Ye nta gahinda, n’uburuhukiro bw’umutima, mur’iyi si ntiharimw’ agakiza, mpirwa ndi Mu mababa Ye gusa.\bd*
\pc \bdit Munsi y’ayo mababa Ye, havuy’ Urukundo rwinshi, Mu mababa niho nzibera, mu mahor’iteka ryose.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Munsi y’amababa ye niho heza, nzajya mpihish’ ibishuko byose,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Niho buhungiro nta cyampangara,\bd*\bd  nzibanira \bd*\bd na Yes’amahoro\bd*\bd .\bd*
